        <section class="vision">
            <div class="vision-container">
                <div class="vision-content">
                    <h2>What's next?</h2>
                    <p>Like my time at Outsystems, we have a huge growth opportunity. Appsmith has a firm and growing presence in APAC and Europe, and we're starting to see some significant momentum in North America.</p>
                    <p>For a company that's been around for just a few years, the traction is remarkable. We're building something that developers actually want to use—a platform that respects their intelligence while accelerating their productivity.</p>
                    <p>The future of low-code isn't about replacing developers; it's about empowering them with better tools, more transparency, and the freedom to build without constraints.</p>
                </div>
